---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/main.astro';
---

<MainLayout
  title="Patented Liquid Desiccant Technology | Enerama Environmental"
  description="The Dragon Liquid Desiccant platform — PCT patented climate control. 30–70% energy savings, 100+ L/h water recovery, natural pathogen elimination. 14 years field-proven."
  keywords="liquid desiccant, dragon platform, PCT patent, dehumidification, water from air, solar thermal HVAC, industrial climate control"
  canonicalPath="/technology"
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="relative text-white py-20" style="background-color: #0B3D4C;">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-4xl">
        <div class="inline-block px-4 py-2 rounded-full mb-6 text-sm font-medium" style="background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);">
          PCT Patented · Field-Proven Since 2011 · 350+ Units Deployed
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold leading-tight mb-6 text-balance">
          The Dragon™ Liquid Desiccant Platform
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-200 max-w-3xl leading-relaxed">
          A patented climate infrastructure replacing compressor-based HVAC in humidity-critical environments. Independent temperature and humidity control, water recovered from air, natural pathogen elimination — all from one integrated system.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- See Dragon in Action — YouTube video link -->
  <section class="bg-white">
    <div class="w-full">
      <a
        href="https://youtu.be/0FEcOP-OiiA"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        aria-label="See Dragon in Action — opens YouTube video"
        class="relative block group overflow-hidden"
      >
        <img
          src="https://img.youtube.com/vi/0FEcOP-OiiA/maxresdefault.jpg"
          alt="See Dragon in Action — Liquid Desiccant system in industrial deployment"
          class="w-full h-96 object-cover transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:scale-105"
          onerror="this.onerror=null;this.src='https://img.youtube.com/vi/0FEcOP-OiiA/hqdefault.jpg';"
        />
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/30 group-hover:bg-black/40 transition-colors flex items-center justify-center">
          <div class="text-center text-white">
            <div class="w-20 h-20 mx-auto rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4 shadow-2xl group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform" style="background-color: #E07B39;">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 ml-1" fill="white" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path d="M8 5v14l11-7z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold drop-shadow-lg">See Dragon in Action</div>
            <div class="text-sm opacity-90 mt-1">Watch on YouTube</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The Core Principle -->
  <section class="bg-white py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6 text-center" style="color: #1B3A6B;">
          How It Works
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 text-center mb-12 leading-relaxed">
          Conventional HVAC cools air first, then condenses moisture as a side effect. Dragon does the opposite: a concentrated hygroscopic salt solution pulls moisture out of air directly — without compression, without phase change, without the energy cost.
        </p>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4" style="background-color: #0D7377;">1</div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2" style="color: #1B3A6B;">Air Intake</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Ambient air enters the Dragon absorber stage.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4" style="background-color: #0D7377;">2</div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2" style="color: #1B3A6B;">Desiccant Absorption</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Concentrated Liquid Desiccant contacts the air, absorbing water vapor and eliminating pathogens on contact.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4" style="background-color: #0D7377;">3</div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2" style="color: #1B3A6B;">Regeneration</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Diluted solution is heated at 50–70°C — compatible with solar thermal, waste heat, or low-grade sources — driving water back out.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4" style="background-color: #0D7377;">4</div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2" style="color: #1B3A6B;">Water Recovery</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Condensed water collected as a clean byproduct; concentrated solution returns to step 2 in a continuous cycle.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Performance Comparison -->
  <section class="bg-gray-50 py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4" style="color: #1B3A6B;">
          Dragon vs Conventional HVAC
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Measured across 27 projects and 350+ units over 14 years
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="overflow-x-auto">
        <table class="w-full bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm">
          <thead>
            <tr style="background-color: #1B3A6B;">
              <th class="px-6 py-4 text-left text-white font-semibold">Parameter</th>
              <th class="px-6 py-4 text-left text-white font-semibold">Conventional HVAC</th>
              <th class="px-6 py-4 text-left text-white font-semibold">Dragon Liquid Desiccant</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody class="divide-y divide-gray-200">
            <tr>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 font-semibold text-gray-900">Energy consumption</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 text-gray-700">Baseline (100%)</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 font-semibold" style="color: #0D7377;">30–70% less</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 font-semibold text-gray-900">Temperature & humidity control</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 text-gray-700">Coupled (humidity is a side effect)</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 font-semibold" style="color: #0D7377;">Independent, precise</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 font-semibold text-gray-900">Water recovery</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 text-gray-700">None — condensate discarded</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 font-semibold" style="color: #0D7377;">Up to 100+ L/h per unit, clean</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 font-semibold text-gray-900">Pathogen control</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 text-gray-700">Requires UV, chemical disinfectants, or filters</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 font-semibold" style="color: #0D7377;">Natural — desiccant kills pathogens on contact</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 font-semibold text-gray-900">Regeneration heat source</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 text-gray-700">Mechanical compression only</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 font-semibold" style="color: #0D7377;">Solar thermal, waste heat, low-grade heat</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ROI Calculator Placeholder -->
  <section class="bg-white py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4" style="color: #1B3A6B;">
            Typical ROI
          </h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">
            Payback periods across deployed projects
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          <div class="p-8 rounded-lg border-2" style="border-color: #0D7377;">
            <div class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider mb-2" style="color: #0D7377;">Food Processing</div>
            <div class="text-4xl font-bold mb-2" style="color: #1B3A6B;">2–3 yrs</div>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Typical payback for industrial drying and cold-storage retrofits</p>
          </div>

          <div class="p-8 rounded-lg border-2" style="border-color: #E07B39;">
            <div class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider mb-2" style="color: #E07B39;">Agriculture & Greenhouses</div>
            <div class="text-4xl font-bold mb-2" style="color: #1B3A6B;">3–4 yrs</div>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Payback including water-recovery reuse for irrigation</p>
          </div>

          <div class="p-8 rounded-lg border-2" style="border-color: #1B3A6B;">
            <div class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider mb-2" style="color: #1B3A6B;">Pharmaceutical / Data Centers</div>
            <div class="text-4xl font-bold mb-2" style="color: #1B3A6B;">4–5 yrs</div>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Regulated environments where pathogen control adds compliance value</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="text-center text-gray-600 mt-8 text-sm">
          ROI depends on facility size, outdoor climate, existing HVAC efficiency, and local energy costs.
          Our engineering team provides project-specific analysis during consultation.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Patent Protection -->
  <section class="py-20" style="background-color: #1B3A6B;">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
        <div class="inline-block px-4 py-2 rounded-full mb-6 text-sm font-semibold" style="background-color: rgba(224, 123, 57, 0.2); color: #E07B39;">
          INTELLECTUAL PROPERTY
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6 text-white">
          PCT Patent Protected Platform
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-200 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
          The Dragon platform is protected by trade secrets accumulated over 14 years of continuous field operation and a PCT patent covering the next-generation Solar TES integration, filed Q1 2026.
        </p>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm p-6 rounded-lg border border-white/20 text-left">
            <div class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider mb-2" style="color: #E07B39;">Core Platform</div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-white">Dragon Liquid Desiccant</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm leading-relaxed">
              Trade secrets, proprietary salt formulations, and 14 years of operational data. Not reproducible without years of real-world deployment.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm p-6 rounded-lg border border-white/20 text-left">
            <div class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider mb-2" style="color: #E07B39;">Next Generation</div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-white">Dragon Solar TES</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm leading-relaxed">
              PCT patent filed Q1 2026. Thermal energy storage module enables fully renewable 24/7 Dragon operation. Pre-commercial development.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="bg-white py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6" style="color: #1B3A6B;">
        See Dragon in Your Environment
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Our engineering team designs a custom Dragon configuration for your facility and provides a complete performance & ROI analysis.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a
          href="/contact"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 text-base font-semibold text-white rounded-lg shadow-lg hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity"
          style="background-color: #E07B39;"
        >
          Request Technical Consultation
        </a>
        <a
          href="/products"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 text-base font-semibold rounded-lg border-2 hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity"
          style="border-color: #1B3A6B; color: #1B3A6B;"
        >
          Explore Product Range
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>
